.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, indie, funk, reggae
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, volleyball, baseball, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the fan of reggae is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the far right##1
4. the fan of indie is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
5. the fan of funk is between the fan of folk and the fan of indie##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | indie     | funk           | folk | reggae  |
| Sport         | water-polo | ice-hockey | volleyball   | baseball |

