.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, d&b, funk, hip-hop
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, helicopter, scooter, tram
1. the fan of d&b is the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
5. the fan of indie is between the person driving the van and the fan of funk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | d&b | indie | funk      |
| Transport     | scooter | van    | helicopter  | tram |

