.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, handball, tennis, basketball
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, van, bus, jet-ski
1. the person driving the car is the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person driving the van is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person driving the bus##2
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the car is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | baseball | basketball | tennis     | handball   |
| Transport   | bus   | van     | jet-ski | car |

