.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, pilot, photographer, fisherman
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, taxi, helicopter, skateboard
1. the photographer is between the person driving the car and the engineer##2
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the engineer##1
3. the fisherman is on the right of the engineer##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the engineer is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | pilot | photographer | engineer | fisherman |
| Transport   | car         | skateboard       | taxi    | helicopter         |

