.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, asparagus, kiwi, zucchini
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, water-polo, soccer, parkour
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
3. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person eating asparagus and the person who's sport is parkour##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | zucchini   | kiwi      | asparagus   | spinach  |
| Sport   | parkour | water-polo | soccer | skateboarding |

