.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: potato, strawberry, watermelon, mango
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, satire, martial-arts, zombie
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person eating strawberry is between the person eating mango and the person eating potato##2
3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | potato     | strawberry | mango   | watermelon        |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | martial-arts   | satire | zombie |

