.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, video-games, dancing, hiking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, reggae, ambient, house
1. the fan of ambient is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of house##1
3. the fan of electronic is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is the fan of reggae##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the fan of reggae is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | video-games | dancing | hiking | collecting |
| Music-Genre   | ambient          | reggae     | house  | electronic     |

