2. the coach is between the person watching romance movies and the dancer##2
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far right##1
4. the dancer is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | dancer | coach | teacher | security-guard     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie   | spy    | romance   | time-travel |

