The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, car, quad-bike, ship
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the car##1
2. the indian is the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the australian is between the person driving the quad-bike and the colombian##2
4. the indian is on the right of the australian##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | german | colombian | australian | indian |
| Transport     | taxi     | car   | ship | quad-bike  |

