.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, polish, british, colombian
4 different pets are kept: hamster, turtle, rat, frog
1. the indonesian is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
2. the colombian is the owner of the rat##1
3. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the hamster and the polish##2
4. the owner of the frog is the owner of the frog##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | colombian | polish | indonesian | british |
| Pet           | rat  | frog  | turtle | hamster      |

