.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, video-games, cooking, fishing
4 different pets are kept: frog, turtle, bird, lizard
1. the owner of the turtle is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is between the owner of the frog and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | cooking    | fishing     | writing | video-games |
| Pet     | turtle | lizard | bird       | frog     |

 